                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=distdev",
                        "name": "distdev",
                        "displayName": "Andrey Shevchenko",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "It's not a bug, because on 11th iteration you have February 28th (according to start date - 30th and option extend_month == false). So, on next iteration you have March, 28th.\r\nI would suggest to replace your code smth like this:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n$monthCount = 0;\r\nfor($i = 0; $i < 12; $i++) {\r\n    $monthCount++;\r\n}\r\n$date->add($monthCount, Zend_Date::MONTH);\r\n{code}",
